  <name>Singularity</name>
  <summary>No Man's Sky Mod Manager</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Singularity is a comprehensive mod manager for No Man's Sky.
      Browse, install, and manage mods from Nexus Mods.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Browse and install mods from Nexus Mods</li>
      <li>Automatic mod conflict detection</li>
      <li>Easy mod installation and removal</li>
      <li>Cross-platform network compatibility</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
